The paper proposes a novel patient vector learning architecture using unsupervised machine learning algorithms to learn patient representation directly from medical claims data. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), cybernetics (cs.CY), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), healthcare (cs.HC), and computational linguistics (cs.CL) as it involves natural language processing of medical claims data.
